The following features are currently supported:
@itemize @bullet
@item Test module implements test cases
@item Error and exception handling
@item Concurrent test case execution
@item Test Module Template Wizard (createtestmodule)
@item File parsing with MIN Parser
@item Logging facilities for test modules with MIN Logger (currently only limited set of features)
@item Test case synchronization with MIN Event System
@item Write once, test everywhere, that is, test cases made during the development phase can be used in system testing, automatic release testing, and so on
@item Easy to use
@item Multiple test cases can be executed concurrently
@item All execution errors and exceptions are handled properly and reported to teste.
@item Support for test automation
@end itemize
